sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>Jupyter Notebook
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>Cluster / RayJobClient
    participant KueueAPI as Kueue API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant RouteAPI as OpenShift Routes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RayDash as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant RayClient as Ray Client Server<br/>10001/TCP mTLS
    participant SecretsAPI as Kubernetes Secrets<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,SecretsAPI: Flow 1: Cluster Creation

    User->>SDK: ClusterConfiguration(cpu, mem, gpu, ...)
    SDK->>SDK: generate_yaml(config)<br/>Render base-template.yaml
    SDK->>KueueAPI: List LocalQueues<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KueueAPI-->>SDK: Default LocalQueue<br/>(queue-name label)
    SDK->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>(or AppWrapper CR)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: 201 Created
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: Watch event:<br/>new RayCluster
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create Ray head + worker Pods<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount

    Note over User,SecretsAPI: Flow 2: Job Submission

    User->>SDK: RayJobClient.submit_job(entrypoint)
    SDK->>RouteAPI: GET Routes<br/>(discover dashboard URL)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    RouteAPI-->>SDK: ray-dashboard-{name} Route
    SDK->>RayDash: POST /api/jobs/<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OpenShift)
    RayDash-->>SDK: Job ID + Status

    Note over User,SecretsAPI: Flow 3: TLS Certificate Generation

    User->>SDK: generate_tls_cert(cluster_name, ns)
    SDK->>SecretsAPI: GET Secret {name}-ca-secret<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    SecretsAPI-->>SDK: ca.key + ca.crt
    SDK->>SDK: Generate client cert<br/>(RSA 2048, SHA-256)
    SDK-->>User: TLS certs written to<br/>tls-{cluster}-{ns}/
    User->>RayClient: ray://... connect<br/>mTLS with client cert
